BUG-12: Timezone Helper Accepts Invalid Time

Severity: High

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Timezone Helper."

2)Enter an impossible time, such as 17:84.

3)Click "Convert."

Expected Result: An error message "Please enter a valid time" should be displayed.

Actual Result: The app accepts the invalid input and performs a nonsensical calculation.

Evidence: 
 ![Screenshot showing Timezone Helper Accepts Invalid Time](evidence\bug-12-invalid-time.png)